The popular GNOME 3 desktop environment may be used under the {{c|OpenRC}} init system in Gentoo (as well as the default {{c|systemd}}).

Currently, {{c|OpenRC}} interoperability is provided via two distinct approaches:
# [https://blogs.gentoo.org/leio/2019/03/26/gnome-3-30/ Official Gentoo support] is provided for GNOME-3.30+. Installation instructions may be found '''[[GNOME/GNOME_Without_systemd/Gentoo|here]]'''.
# Dantrell provides a set of overlays, targeting GNOME-3.14+, as part of his [https://github.com/dantrell/gentoo-project-gnome-without-systemd GNOME without systemd] project. Installation instructions may be found '''[[GNOME/GNOME_Without_systemd/Dantrell|here]]'''.
